==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsoft
<hw>Un*soft"</hw> <pr>(?; 115)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not soft; hard;
coarse; rough.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Bristles of his beard
<xex>unsoft</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsoft</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unsoft
<hw>Un*soft"</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>uns<?/fte</ets>. See
<er>Un-</er> not, and <er>Soft</er>.]</ety> <def>Not softly.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Great climbers fall <qex>unsoft</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsolder</ent>⟦br⟧
